OL,3,CIt's another hold but Bank of England
OL,4,Csignals August cut is on the cards
OL,6,FNo central bank wants to cut right in
OL,7,Fthe middle of an election campaign,
OL,8,Fsays ITV News Economics Editor Joel
OL,9,FHills
OL,11,FNo one cuts during an election
OL,12,Fcampaign.
OL,14,FThe Bank of England is politically
OL,15,Findependent and determined to be
OL,16,Fperceived as being so.
OL,18,FHad it moved today, the decision to
OL,19,Flower the cost of borrowing would have
OL,20,Fbeen pounced on and used by the
OL,21,Fparties in the tussle for votes.
