OL,3,CIt's another hold but Bank of England
OL,4,Csignals August cut is on the cards
OL,6,FHappily for the Bank, yesterday's
OL,7,Finflation data provided the
OL,8,Fjustification for it to sit on its
OL,9,Fhands.
OL,11,FThe headline annual rate of inflation
OL,12,Ffell to 2% last month - bang on the
OL,13,FBank's target.
OL,15,FBut inflation in the Services sector
OL,16,Fof the economy is running at 5.7% -
OL,17,Fhotter than the Bank forecast and too
OL,18,Fhigh for comfort.
