OL,3,CIt's another hold but Bank of England
OL,4,Csignals August cut is on the cards
OL,6,FThe Bank says the increase in the
OL,7,FNational Living Wage in April helps to
OL,8,Fexplain the overshoot, as companies
OL,9,Fpassed on their costs in the form of
OL,10,Fhigher prices.
OL,12,FAirfares, phone and broadband
OL,13,Fcontracts, water and sewage bills and
OL,14,Frents for council housing also rose by
OL,15,Fmore than expected.
OL,17,FThe Monetary Policy Committee (MPC)
OL,18,Fvoted 7-2 to keep interest rates at
OL,19,F5.25%.
