OL,4,Csignals August cut is on the cards
OL,6,FThe minutes add: "As part of the
OL,7,FAugust round, members of the Committee
OL,8,Fwould consider all of the information
OL,9,Favailable and how this affected the
OL,10,Fassessment that the risks from
OL,11,Finflation persistence were receding".
OL,13,FCentral bankers communicate in a
OL,14,Flanguage which often feels tortured
OL,15,Fand incomprehensible to anyone who is
OL,16,Fnot a central banker or a market
OL,17,Fanalyst, but the signal here, while
OL,18,Fnuanced, seems clear enough.
